      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> soy sauce</strong>, <strong>hoisin sauce</strong> and <strong>toasted sesame oil</strong> to the pan and cook for 2 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p><p>Note: Please make sure you cook your chicken thoroughly (until piping hot!) as cooking equipment varies</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
